snippet: PROFESSIONAL: When was your last period Jane?

PROFESSIONAL: When were you last sexually active?
CUSTOMER: Unsure. A week ago
PROFESSIONAL: Alexis, can you describe your symptoms?
CUSTOMER: Burning when I pee
CUSTOMER: I have to pee every five minutes and I pee very little
CUSTOMER: Pain in bladder area
PROFESSIONAL: Okay, have you been in the sun a lot lately, Kim?
CUSTOMER: No not at all
PROFESSIONAL: What were you taking Fluconazole, Phenazopyridine and Macrodantin for?
